{"tid":2339845,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［死都唔封大陸吹呀］外國返港隔離「加監」至21日","createTime":"2020-12-25T03:50:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-25T06:22:19.000Z","uid":1550,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d9a7cd9e90c9105670263ea9fbba40aa6686a77e","tid":2339845,"uid":1550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T03:50:01.000Z","msg":"【本報訊】英國公佈在兩名南非武漢肺炎患者中發現另一款傳播力更強的變種病毒後，政府昨晚刊憲進一步收緊邊境防疫規定，今日起所有由外國返港人士，不論經機場或陸路口岸入境，必須到指定檢疫酒店強制檢疫21天，即所有由外國返港人士一律加監至21日；而除早前已宣佈的英國外，於登機當天或之前21天曾逗留南非超過兩小時者，不會獲准登機前來香港。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201225/5UANMF4DOZHJ5KA634GKB7ZE3Q/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201225%2F5UANMF4DOZHJ5KA634GKB7ZE3Q%2F&d=z%2FAKp4ZZwI77wMFl%2FSXGt1RUXPbyrNnFnNFpNAJjDn8%3D&h=2a974e3e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201225%2F5UANMF4DOZHJ5KA634GKB7ZE3Q%2F&h=1c3e3d36\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201225/5UANMF4DOZHJ5KA634GKB7ZE3Q/</a>"},{"pid":"aebe8187913caf1285d9c57a55f77b4459998454","tid":2339845,"uid":260694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T04:07:26.000Z","msg":"大陸封香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/catxm/unwell.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a30af90c6437d6a9b15ab1036f7367ab4dba41d8","tid":2339845,"uid":263349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T06:22:19.000Z","msg":"唔完全封 點控制呀 久唔久又黎一輪"}]}